## Outlier



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
lim_inf <- q1 - 1.5 * estadisticos$RIC
lim_sup <- q3 + 1.5 * estadisticos$RIC

outliers <- datos_curso %>% 
  filter(altura < lim_inf | altura > lim_sup)


gt(outliers)%>%
  gt_theme_excel()
```

